 There is a wide button in the top right of your drscheme window. Click
 it.
 
 When iconify a window (and maybe in other situations) that button is
 implicitly pressed. This is a bug... it's fixed in our CVS versions,
 but not in time for v205.
 
 Sorry for the trouble.
 
